text.tspan: Each colored cicle is a weight of neuron with id 2 in output layer
to change 2 to another neuron use choice variable in scripts/nw.asy.
Eanch 2D pattern represent weights of each of 19 neuroins
in middle layer. Weight ordered in way that corresponds
input pixel order thus alowing to study recognition patterns of
Positive weights have red coloring, negative have blue.
